StructureDefinition: CHEMEDCompositionPharmaceuticalAdvice

Definition of the composition for the pharmaceutical advice document

The official URL for this profile is: 

http://fhir.ch/ig/ch-emed/StructureDefinition/ch-emed-composition-pharmaceuticaladvice
